Job Description
Job Description
Linux Porting, Linux Device Driver experience, VxWorks BSP Development, Embedded Software Developer, Device Driver Engineer
What you need for this position
3 to 8 years hands-on experience in OS Porting and developing drivers for Operating Systems Linux / VxWorks.
You are an expert in Porting OSes Wind River Linux (or) VxWorks to Embedded Boards with Power PC / Intel (x86) architecture.
Domain and working knowledge in Wind River Linux and VxWorks Device drivers is definitely an advantage.
You are an expert in C
Comfortable in working with new hardware and debugging software on it
Engineering degree in Computer Science, Electronics, or related field
